page.title: 17POLICE./WILDLIFE.
page.content: When people are arrested they are aken to a police station.They are charged put into cells.Their meals are rom the canteen at the police station. PC Mitchell is a village policeman,he looks after five villages which are Somersham,Often,Willisham,Nettlestead and Flowton --------------------------------------- WILDLIFE As seen on a mornings walk with Jeremy Davy.Gipping Valley Warden. Animals:hare,rabbit. Birds:kestral,swift,swallow,white throat,blue tit,great tit,yellow hammer;wagtail,dunnock,robin;sparrow. Trees:oak,holly,hawthorne,sycamore, horse chestnut,sweet chestnut,field maple,dog rose . Flowers:yellow archangel,dogs mercury,bluebells,primroses,cowslips, lords and ladies,orchids.
